        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Captive Commuter Toll Relief Act</b></p> <p>This bill modifies the limitations on the use of highway toll revenues to include toll discounts or rebates for use of a toll facility that has no reasonable alternative transportation method.</p>]]></text>
